cat << EOF
Compatible with:

    Bonjour
    Avahi

Compared to some other Zeroconf/Bonjour/Avahi Python packages, python-zeroconf:

    isn't tied to Bonjour or Avahi
    doesn't use D-Bus
    doesn't force you to use particular event loop or Twisted
    is pip-installable
    has PyPI distribution
